{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775820302761,"sessionID":"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV","part":{"id":"prt_d7723658a001sO9AXKTy1EwNyE","messageID":"msg_d77234e15001PvNsGzmRbJjVam","sessionID":"ses_288dd0034ffe7A3MpJOphMOwjV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ff9f80f635334cec9cb6da18","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: <!-- TODO: 填写变更概述 -->\n6: \n7: ## 元信息\n8: \n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n10: - **Language**: Go\n11: - **Size**: L\n12: \n13: ## 目的\n14: \n15: <!-- TODO: 填写变更目的 -->\n16: \n17: ## 范围\n18: \n19: ### 包含\n20: \n21: <!-- TODO: 填写包含范围 -->\n22: \n23: ### 不包含\n24: \n25: <!-- TODO: 填写不包含范围 -->\n26: \n27: ## 影响分析\n28: \n29: ### 直接影响\n30: \n31: <!-- TODO: 填写直接影响的组件 -->\n32: \n33: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n34: \n35: <!-- TODO: 填写下游依赖 -->\n36: \n37: ### 无影响的组件\n38: \n39: <!-- TODO: 填写无影响的组件 -->\n40: \n41: ## 备选方案\n42: \n43: <!-- TODO: 填写备选方案及决策理由 -->\n44: \n45: ## 验收标准\n46: \n47: <!-- TODO: 填写验收标准 -->\n48: \n49: ## 状态\n50: \n51: - [ ] 提案审查\n52: - [ ] 实现\n53: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写变更概述 -->\n\n## 元信息\n\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: L\n\n## 目的\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写变更目的 -->\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775820302752,"end":1775820302760}}}}
